#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "⚠️ Sensitive Content Notice"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This module includes content that may be sensitive. You can check it out by yourself first. This will prepare you well for sharing the content with your teen and others afterwards.\n"
"\n"
"If you need support, see the “Support Contacts” section in your Library for help."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today’s topic is dealing with crises.\n"
"\n"
"All families face crises. When we prepare together and know where to get help before something happens, we can handle it more calmly and confidently.\n"
"\n"
"Crises can be scary, but you can get through them together."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can skills to handle crises help your family? Click play to find out"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today's topic is dealing with crises.\n"
"\n"
"Crisis may occur anywhere. Crisis may occur anytime. Therefore, it is important as a family to have plans in place should any family member find themselves in a crisis situation.\n"
"\n"
"It is important to have plans so that every family member may feel protected.\n"
"\n"
"When we are dealing with crises, remember to take a pause, breathe and keep yourself calm. That will help you to deal with crises better."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Every crisis is a challenge, but it is also a chance to grow stronger as a family and show your teen that together, you can get through anything."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_9.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.media_female_9.name and her teen learned to handle crises together. Hear their story"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"My teen used to be so angry all the time. He would never listen and we would get into big arguments every day. Through @global.app_name, I started spending more time with my teen and strengthening our relationship. One day he shared with me that he was part of a gang but he wanted to get out.\n"
"\n"
"We made short-term and long-term plans together on how we could do that. Our life looks so different now!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name:
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Crisis can happen to anyone.\n"
"\n"
"Let's see what happened with @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name and her granddaughter, @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name:"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Shame my dear, you look really upset, do you want to tell me what happened?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It’s that man, he… he… he touched me."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "(🤔_thinking_) Take a deep breath... What does my child need? She needs me to be calm and listen."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Come and sit down next to me. Take your time, I am listening."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It is true, he… he… made me do it! He made me have sex with him! I did not want to, I swear, and I even said NO, but he told me I would be in trouble."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you for sharing this with me. You are not in trouble. This is not your fault."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yesterday when you went to see your friend. He just came and that’s when it happened."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It is okay, I believe you my child. This is a big thing and we will find a way to get the help we need. Where could we go for help?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My school?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ah I know, let’s go to the clinic. They will know what we can do to help you. Does that sound okay to you?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes… Okay… But will you come with me?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name? should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Of course I will. And @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name? Remember this is not your fault. I love you. You are a good person. We will get through this."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name!
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This was such a difficult situation for @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name and @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name! And this can happen to other girls, and boys too.\n"
"\n"
"Thankfully, @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name gave great support to @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name. Let's think about what she did well."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What skills did @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name use?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Take a deep breath and pause before responding"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Listen to your teen"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Praise your teen for sharing"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Use problem solving skills"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Work out where you can get help"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, @data.characters.f2_grandmother.name actually used all those skills – and so can you!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Crisis can make us feel angry or helpless. But this is when our teens really need us to breathe, listen and think. \n"
"\n"
"Here are some tips to help you deal with a crisis!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "CONNECT"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Make sure your teen knows they can talk to you about anything that happens online and offline, and if a crisis happens, you will handle it together."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "BREATHE"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Stay calm. Ask yourself, \"What does my teen need right now?\""
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "LISTEN"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tell them you are there for them and love them."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "THINK"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talk with your teen. What might help the situation? Reach out to the available support around you, in your community, and online."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You might need to make immediate plans now and then long-term plans later. Remember, you can find Support Contacts in the @global.app_name Library."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"It is helpful to practise dealing with crises before something happens.\n"
"\n"
"Let's look at five family crisis examples together. Imagine you are the parent: What would you do?\n"
"\n"
"Remember: CONNECT - BREATHE - LISTEN - THINK"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_15.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_15.name?
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Crisis 1: @data.characters.f2_son_15.name fights at school.\n"
"\n"
"How could you respond to @data.characters.f2_son_15.name?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I have never done this before. And now they will expel me."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name?
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Crisis 2: @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name gets pregnant.\n"
"\n"
"How could you respond to @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Father, I am so ashamed. I do not know what to do."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name?
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Crisis 3: @data.characters.f1_son_18.name makes a girl pregnant.\n"
"\n"
"How could you respond to @data.characters.f1_son_18.name?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I do not want to have a baby."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Crisis 4: Someone in the family may get sick.\n"
"\n"
"How could you respond in this situation?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The test said I have HIV. I am scared I am going to die."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name?
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Crisis 5: @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name is pressured into sex by her boyfriend.\n"
"\n"
"How could you respond to @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandmother.role_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I didn't really want to. Now I will get pregnant or be ill. @data.characters.f2_grandmother.role_name, I am so scared..."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "This week's home activity is to look back at the five crisis examples and discuss what you would do together if this happened to a friend or in your family."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_15.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Choose one example to discuss with your teen:** \n"
"\n"
"- Crisis 1: @data.characters.f2_son_15.name fights at school\n"
"- Crisis 2: @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name gets pregnant\n"
"- Crisis 3: @data.characters.f1_son_18.name makes a girl pregnant\n"
"- Crisis 4: Someone in the family may get sick\n"
"- Crisis 5: @data.characters.f2_daughter_19.name is pressured into sex by her boyfriend\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"**And remember:**\n"
"😌 BREATHE: Stay calm \n"
"👂🏾 LISTEN: Assure your teen you are there for them\n"
"💭 THINK: What might help this situation?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you chat with your teen about how you could respond to a crisis together?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's wonderful! Talking about this now will help your teen feel supported and safe. You are doing great."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Give it a try! It can feel hard, but even just thinking about it and starting the conversation together is already a big step."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's completely okay - talking about potential crises can feel overwhelming. Keep spending time with your teen, and come back to this when it feels right."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember to support and encourage each other. It is hard to remain calm and listen to each other in a crisis - you can be proud of yourself."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_daughter_12.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.media_daughter_12.name overcame a difficult crisis with the help of her mother. Tap play to learn how"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Two years ago, I was raped by my uncle who stayed in our yard. I did not tell my mother, because I was afraid she would hit me, shout at me, or even throw me out of the house. I did not have anywhere else to go.\n"
"\n"
"When my mother started with @global.app_name, we started spending more time together. I was still afraid, but in the end I shared it with my mother. My mom did not shout, but she listened and told me it is not my fault. We went to the police and the clinic together. I am so grateful I do not have to carry this secret anymore."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Well done for taking time for yourself today. 🎉"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here is a short video to help you slow down before you go"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When everything feels like it is falling apart And you can't help but raise your voice When all the frustrations are beginning to start Remember that you have a choice\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"You can take pause, you can count to 10 Play a game or do something fun You can phone a friend, someone to confide in Remember you're not the only one\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more Because I really couldn't love you more"
msgstr ""
